America's Test Kitchen AP GF Flour Blend

24 oz (4 1/2 c + 1/3 c) white rice flour
7 1/2 oz (1 2/3 c) brown rice flour
7 oz (1 1/3 c) potato starch
3 oz (3/4 c) tapioca starch
3/4 oz (1/4 c) nonfat dry milk powder

Whisk all ingredients together in large bowl until well combined. Transfer to airtight container and refrigerate for up to 3 months.

Notes: Be sure to use potato starch not potato flour. Tapioca starch and flour are interchangeable.
